				<article id="post-2" class="post-2 page type-page status-publish hentry">

					<div class="entry-content">
						<h1>THE BEER HERE<br />
IS NEAR &amp; DEAR</h1>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5" src="http://baerlicbrewing.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/Baerlic_Imperial_vs_Tulip.jpg" alt="Glasses full of Baerlic Beer" width="578" height="457" /></p>
<p>Translating to ‘of barley’ in old english, bærlic reiterates the fundamental idea that all things, no matter how complex or involved, can always be traced backward to a single, simple core or point of view.</p>
<p>Our point of view comes from a belief that we are all in this together and that our actions shape our world – by being honest, we are approachable; by being consistent, we are trusted; by being considerate, we can sleep at night; and by choosing to keep it simple, we are able to do this really well.</p>
<p><a href="http://eepurl.com/clT-wj">New Beer Releases &#8211; Get Email Updates</a></p>

					</div><!-- .entry-content -->

				</article><!-- #post -->

			
				</div>

			





			


