									<h4>Pre-Prohibition Lager</h4>

						 			<p>Brewed with flaked corn reminiscent of your great great grandpappy's favorite chuggin' beer from the 1880s but with notes of ripe fruit, fresh spring flowers and a touch of citrus in a beer made for drinkin'!</p>

