				<article id="post-106" class="post-106 page type-page status-publish hentry">

					<div class="entry-content">
						<h1 style="text-align: center;">BAERLIC BEERS OUT IN THE WILD</h1>
<p style="text-align: left;">Unlike most breweries, we self-distribute our beer throughout the Portland metro area. That means that all the hard work of relationship building and maintenance (we love our accounts!), account management (staying organized) and beer delivery (actual heavy lifting) we do ourselves. We believe this keeps us more connected with the end consumer (you) and let&#8217;s us speak more clearly for ourselves. So, in addition to our taproom, you’ll find Baerlic beers at these Portland area bars, restaurants and other fine establishments.</p>
<p><iframe src="https://mapsengine.google.com/map/u/0/embed?mid=z_7hsuXcTXQ0.kaKsiiDAR87c" height="500" width="100%" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>

					</div><!-- .entry-content -->

				</article><!-- #post -->

			
